prove:
    abstract_prop q(x, y, z)

    prop p(x, y R):
        x > y
        forall t R:
            $q(x, y, t)

    have a, b R

    know $p(a, b)

    a > b

    $q(a, b, 2)

prove:
    abstract_prop p(a)

    have b R, c R

    know forall a R:
        $p(a + b)
        =>:
            $p(a)

    know $p(c + b)

    $p(c)